BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 620.50 Tm (deploy approvals, security & licensing rules, and approved tools. Developers rotate) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 606.00 Tm (between clients and mix up the rules. Ask *"Can I use a GPL library?"* and the) Tj ET
