BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 562.50 Tm (limits each developer to the client they are authorized for.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 68.00 543.00 Tm (All data is synthetic. No real, proprietary, or personally identifiable data is used.) Tj ET
